{"tid":1308351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廢老天堂】人在中國丢個垃圾也要照臉評分！","createTime":"2019-07-12T01:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T11:14:26.000Z","uid":35519,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"511792b720f58e6daf4672a87dcadce7b5a535c9","tid":1308351,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:06:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[爆卦] 人在中國丢個垃圾也要照臉評分！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1562859298.A.E79.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1562859298.A.E79.html&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0Ftn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=399e820b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1562859298.A.E79.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">中國人臉科技好棒棒，照照臉就能結婚！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4iOBgea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4iOBgea.jpg&h=544607f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">上廁所也要照照臉，文明好先進！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MepHAoA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMepHAoA.jpg&h=20cc98a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來！照一張。不爽照就甭上廁所了！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ax3W3nU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAx3W3nU.jpg&h=9ed7e41a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VVKQmXG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVVKQmXG.jpg&h=daab314f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">還有更棒的，<br />\n丢垃圾也要照照臉！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/S9kkP8K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FS9kkP8K.jpg&h=33be054a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/O4S9FhS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FO4S9FhS.jpg&h=fd9e762d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>照完臉，才能丟垃圾。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VVKQmXG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVVKQmXG.jpg&h=daab314f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n別忘了，領垃圾袋也要登記，憑卡領取！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ybewi6D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fybewi6D.jpg&h=0a77ca05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真是生活智慧王，看你丟垃圾能得幾分！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FIAllAo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFIAllAo.jpg&h=e3957641&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8e8567d5cbd771cfa9fb900617c4f30e089bac5","tid":1308351,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:07:36.000Z","msg":"[五毛分化警示] 散佈失敗論，叫人聚焦，放棄其他野，去金鐘，乃一貫分化技倆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日突然多左好多風向話區區遊行無用，連儂牆無用，其實咁先代表佢地仲係好有用，大家唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共產黨其實怕我地搞地區工作多過出金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304935\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"423fda14332fc0f87fd04ce22b1ca716f4c82b1c"